channel.title: Women Arrested
channel.description:
I Recently found this on another website.
Woman accused of having sex with boy, 14 The Camano Island woman reportedly moved to the Midwest to be nearer the boy.
By Scott Pesznecker Herald Writer
A Camano Island woman accused of having sex with a 14-year-old boy she met over the Internet was arrested Monday when she moved to the Midwest to live closer to him.
Police found Julie Ann Welborn, 38, at a Red Roof Inn in Jackson Township, about 50 miles south of Cleveland. A U-Haul truck containing her belongings was parked outside.
She faces charges in Massillon Municipal Court of unlawful sex with a minor and using telecommunications to solicit sex from a minor. She was being held Wednesday in Stark County Jail on $500,000 bail.
Welborn and the 14-year-old boy met through an online role-playing game called RuneScape, a game played by more than 100,000 people, according to its Web site.
The boy was 12 when they first made contact online a little more than a year ago.
Welborn allegedly had sex with the boy in October when she traveled to Ohio to meet him in person.
And i'll leave it at that, just to warn you guys there are strange people online
